belongs_to_collection.name: Soubrettes Services : Tous les films de la série Soubrettes Services

overview: For this new opus devoted to French maids, Hervé Bodilis calls on the stars to wear the outfit: small black dresses, aprons and white headdresses. In the hotel where they work, these maids show themselves up to their reputation by satisfying all the requests of the customers, giving themselves fully to the males who desire them.
title: Anna's French Maid Service
